reviewText: This would have been a big waste of money if I didn't get her videos from the library. This one in particular has only a few "exercises" on them and all the are is yoga - very common traditional yoga postures that she makes it seem like are her creations. She knows her stuff, but come on, put more on here than 4 yoga poses and make sure you give proper credit to the ancient system from which these come.
Very good guided stretches to restore flexibility.  She also understands how you got stiff and why the stretches work to reverse that.  Very good info..
